metadata.name: Most Sanctioned #1
metadata.description: Call Putin's Bluff and Help Ukraine. The 52 NFTs in this collection shine light on the people sanctioned by world governments for enabling Putin and benefiting from his war of aggression against Ukraine. This NFT poker card will be revealed 1 week after mint. Those sanctioned include oligarchs, government officials, military generals, media, and members of Putin's inner circle. 50 percent of royalties will be donated to projects helping Ukraine.
